_pathToFile: path to the original .arb/.json file, for example 'arb.gen/content.json' ==[_DEFAULT_PATH]
_outputClass: Name of output class localization be defaul $L
_lDirName: The name of the directory where all dart localization files will reside. By by default  `lib/localization`
_arbName: Filename for the source file after translating. The files are located in the l10n directory.
_preferredLanguage: preferredLanguage must be null or one of `translateTo`
_baseLanguage: optional language of source wich you prefer to translate
